{"tid":1494093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又黎啦又黎啦，左膠癌上腦班人又捉鬼啦","createTime":"2019-08-21T13:50:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T17:41:58.000Z","uid":26491,"like":39,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a7c6d5b9a73a520996b7992263a6f88bd24ea179","tid":1494093,"uid":26491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:50:08.000Z","msg":"睇下連登啲post?<br />\n全部都話前面嗰啲係鬼<br />\n又話低質示威者乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n俾左膠揸旗一次活動<br />\n全部人嘅左膠癌上腦上撚到呢<br />\n起鐵馬都變埋鬼<br />\n<br />\n距離勇武心灰意冷收皮不遠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n泛民大成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3770f15447c4b25e78284c9a6b0da09615ece004","tid":1494093,"uid":38784,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:52:18.000Z","msg":"黑警成功左了<br />\n個個都自己分化自己友 自己唔想衝就唔比人地衝 驚既咪自己走先 <br />\n不分化 不割席 不篤灰 實行左2個月 宜家比班狗搞一搞 就冇左呢回事 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0470492e868e6c4e1091bbddd84c6729f01df535","tid":1494093,"uid":26491,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:52:23.000Z","msg":"只係俾左膠揸一次旗咁大把<br />\n即刻成個活動就推左去雨傘後期<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb8f9ebf8dd87a5a94e55c5bbcfbb997a32ce4d","tid":1494093,"uid":26491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3770f15447c4b25e78284c9a6b0da09615ece004","tid":1494093,"uid":38784,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T13:52:18.000Z","msg":"黑警成功左了<br />\n個個都自己分化自己友 自己唔想衝就唔比人地衝 驚既咪自己走先 <br />\n不分化 